g.aria-label: If you passed more orange signs than yellow signs in the last step, count the number of rectangular signs you passed in the last step, and skip that many steps. If you are currently facing the Way of the Horse, go to step 14; otherwise, make a U-turn and drive forward as far as you can. Go the Way of the Cow for as far as you can. Turn left and drive a block, then do those two actions again. Then count the number of letters on the most recent sign with letters you passed, and go to that step.
Wow, those signs were enthralling! When you get home, you're so excited you decide you want to do some research on their official categorization.
